headline: myFICO Sees Significant Surge in Consumers Checking FICO Scores
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., April 01, 2025--In honor of National Financial Literacy Month, global analytics software leader FICO (NYSE: FICO) is encouraging consumers to take charge of their financial well-being by checking their FICO速 Scores for free at myFICO.com/free. As more people recognize the importance of understanding their credit health, FICO has seen a nearly 70% increase in users accessing their FICO速 Score 8 for free via myFICO over the past year.
